//Engels fragment info Information New-West district is and will continue in the coming years. In the physical area, after years of rest, much is happening again.\n\n For example, the city has made available 40 million for a public space refurbishment (in selected areas). New West is one of these. However, it is a requirement that residents get control of how this turnaround should come true. Now its happening on the basis of days of consultation. However, the experience is that few people get here.
\n\nFor this problem statement, we thought that a mobile application could provide an outcome. The application consists of a number of components. This will keep you informed of all events around Amsterdam New West with the free news articles. This news is limited to New West. The news articles are gathered directly from The Parools website.
\n\nTo make the users more aware of their environment and the changes they can bring, weve made a survey. There are open questions, such as what part of the city they want to see a renewal. This information is stored in our database. Then this information can be sent to the municipality of Amsterdam. With this information, they get an insight into what the residents want to change.
